OL,3,CMatthew Kelly and Denise Welch star in
OL,4,CManchester play
OL,6,FVideo report by Caroline Whitmore
OL,8,FAward-winning Lancashire playwright
OL,9,FJim Cartwright is famous for penning
OL,10,Fthe popular play Road and The Rise and
OL,11,FFall of Little Voice, along with many
OL,12,Fothers.
OL,14,FNow, almost forty years after he
OL,15,Fpenned Road, he has written a brand
OL,16,Fnew play which has its world premiere
OL,17,Fat Hope Mill Theatre in Manchester.
OL,19,FIt stars popular actors and presenters
OL,20,FMatthew Kelly and Denise Welch - the
OL,21,Fonly two roles in the show.
