OL,3,CMatthew Kelly and Denise Welch star in
OL,4,CManchester play
OL,6,FThe Gap delves into the audacious
OL,7,Fadventures of Walter and Corral. He's
OL,8,Fback up north, she's still down south.
OL,9,FThey haven't seen each other for 50
OL,10,Fyears, not since their Soho days, back
OL,11,Fin the swinging '60s.
OL,13,FHowever, a chance phone call reunites
OL,14,Fthem for one magical night and in next
OL,15,Fto no time, they're back to their old
OL,16,Ftricks.
OL,18,FIn the role of Walter, Matthew Kelly
OL,19,Fis one of the UK's most beloved stars
OL,20,Fof stage and screen.
