OL,3,CMatthew Kelly and Denise Welch star in
OL,4,CManchester play
OL,6,FAlongside her decade-spanning acting
OL,7,Fcareer, Denise has been a regular
OL,8,Fpanellist on ITV's Loose Women since
OL,9,F2001.
OL,11,FJim said: This is a new play called
OL,12,FThe Gap about a couple who haven't
OL,13,Fseen each other for 50 years. They
OL,14,Flive at different sides of the country
OL,15,Fand a chance phone call brings them
OL,16,Ftogether.
