OL,3,CMatthew Kelly and Denise Welch star in
OL,4,CManchester play
OL,6,F"I wanted to write something about
OL,7,Fgenerational gaps. The gap between the
OL,8,Fnorth and the south.J"We're here at
OL,9,FHope Mill theatre in Ancoats which I
OL,10,Fthink is the most exciting theatre in
OL,11,FManchester easily."
OL,13,FMatthew Kelly said: "Well, because
OL,14,Fit's only the two of us you know,
OL,15,Fyou've got to get on because the play
OL,16,Fis about two friends who've not seen
OL,17,Feach other for 50 years!"
