OL,3,CMatthew Kelly and Denise Welch star in
OL,4,CManchester play
OL,6,FDenise said: "We're honoured to be
OL,7,Fdoing the world premiere of a new Jim
OL,8,FCartwright play. Having both worked
OL,9,Fwith him before, he's fantastic.
OL,11,F"It's not without its challenges.
OL,12,FThere is a poetry to Jim's work. I
OL,13,Fknow you get used to doing it a
OL,14,Fcertain way in a rehearsal room.
OL,16,F"Then you come in to tech rehearsals,
OL,17,Fand there's some sentences, like,
OL,18,Fnothing could suit us old and we
OL,19,Fcouldn't remember it."
