OL,6,FJim added: "You know, I never do get
OL,7,Fnervous before - because it's kind of
OL,8,Fout of my hands. I get excited, though
OL,9,FI can't wait for everyone to see it
OL,10,Fnow."
OL,12,FThe Gap is playing at Hope Mill
OL,13,FTheatre in Ancoats until the 16 March.
